<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  {{>bootstrapAndBasicHeader}}
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/index.css">
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <img src="/image/logo-with-name.png">
    <a href="/users/register" id="sign-up">
      <div>Sign up</div>
    </a>
    <a href="/users/login" id="sign-in">
      <div>Sign in</div>
    </a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img class="d-block w-50 carousel-img" src="/image/administrativeWork.png" alt="First slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            {{!-- <h5>This is the 1st heading</h5>
            <p>Showing some functionality</p> --}}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-50 carousel-img" src="/image/reports.jpg" alt="Second slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            {{!-- <h5>This is the 2nd heading</h5> --}}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-50 carousel-img" src="/image/onlineMeeting.png" alt="Third slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            {{!-- <h5>This is the 3rd heading</h5>
            <p>Showing some functionality</p> --}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="dialogue">
      <p>Upgrade the way you manage!!<br> JOIN US</p>
    </section>

    <section class="article">
      <article>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/teacherFeedback.png">
            <h4>Feedback on the way</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Teachers can provide lecture specific visual feedback, representing students feedback such as behaviour,
               frequency of answers and so on.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/meetings.png">
            <h4>Meetings</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Meetings play a vital role in today's internet world, so hold tight to schedule one.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/parentTeacherConnect.png">
            <h4>Parents are in sync</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Parents receive weekly reports which consist of attendance, marks and special comments from teacher for space of 
              improval.
            </p>
          </div>
          {{!--
        </div>
        <div class="row"> --}}
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/studentStaff.png">
            <h4>Single source no redundancy</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Add or remove student and staff is clicks away so that the correct people have correct rights to perform 
              activity</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/financeManagement.gif">
            <h4>The revenue</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Fetch the overview of income and expenses within a click and balance the right entity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img src="/image/attendance.gif">
            <h4>Students attendance</h4>
            <br>
            <p>Students attendance is recorded and can be exported, no need to maintain a diary or an excel sheet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
  {{>footers}}
  
</body>

